Text: It's a story about a girl who fall in love with a boy living in France through
  social media and the bond she holds for him was incredible for this she left everything
  in her home country including her career, family, friends, dreams and begins her
  journey to France.She spends everything just to reach to her love but after reaching
  there is story of her emotions which is to continue.......her love whether she got
  it or not and but she faced there which made her .....
